China's Guangzhou city government has been recruiting 50 students from Sandu County, Guizhou Province, every year, since 2018 to study at the Guangdong Lingnan Modern Technician College, with tuition fee reductions, free dormitories, as well as training in e-commerce livestreaming. How will these programs support Guangzhou as one of the biggest livestream powerhouses in the country? CGTN's Zhu Zhu reports.